    /**
     * errno : 0
     * data : {"searchArr":["研究发现：阿司匹林可降低消化道癌风险","世卫称三个月全球新冠病例增五倍"],"newsArr":[{"id":1,"state":1,"pic":[""],"title":"测试广告1","type":"2","url":"https://www.baidu.com/"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":604,"pic":["https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/a07f7c31p00qevp2s00psc000sw00e3c.png"],"title":"戚薇P出逆天长腿回应工作室P图技术 这波操作够机灵","type":"1","content":"<div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"page js-page on\">\n              <p>今早，戚薇的\u201c大长腿\u201d被上了热搜，结果却引来了戚薇本人的极度不满！<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/e89dd34fj00qevo2i000wc000c800icc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/e89dd34fj00qevo2i000wc000c800icc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/f307f56cj00qevo2i000tc000c800icc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/f307f56cj00qevo2i000tc000c800icc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>戚薇本人吐槽自己的工作室P图P过了，并自己动手P出逆天长腿幽默回应工作室，戚哥也真是的real豪爽了。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/7ca3dac5p00qevo3200a6c000hb00nec.png\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/7ca3dac5p00qevo3200a6c000hb00nec.png'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>其实戚薇机场穿搭图咱们基本也能天天见，每次的造型和街拍图也是超有\u201c料\u201d的那种，比如说这样的：<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/9c04f985j00qevoa70036c000sg0175c.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/9c04f985j00qevoa70036c000sg0175c.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>这样的：<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/1672deb8j00qevoal00awc000sg016oc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/1672deb8j00qevoal00awc000sg016oc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/490cd31ej00qevoal00asc000sg016oc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/490cd31ej00qevoal00asc000sg016oc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>还有这样的：<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/8fddc5b3j00qevob2002uc000sg016oc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/8fddc5b3j00qevob2002uc000sg016oc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/39b28505j00qevob2003oc000sg016oc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/39b28505j00qevob2003oc000sg016oc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><\/div><div class=\"page js-page\"><p>这次戚薇的穿搭依然酷飒无比，她的街拍穿搭的确是教科书级别。只是这次工作室P图失真，让戚薇没忍住直接微博吐槽啦。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/f254322dj00qevo4v001ic000ly00goc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/f254322dj00qevo4v001ic000ly00goc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>随后戚薇工作室满满求生欲回复P图真相，\u201c今天的大长腿并没修长，是用的广角拍的，所以原图就这。。。么长\u201d，还一脸的委屈模样。不得不称赞下戚薇的整个团队真是有趣又机灵呢！<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/2b78d726p00qevoel002nc000c6008dc.png\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/2b78d726p00qevoel002nc000c6008dc.png'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>其实，每一次明星们的街拍图都不是大家看到的那么简单，只要有一点疏忽就会被网友们诟病，做一个精致的女明星真不是你想的那么容易。<\/p>\n              <div class=\"otitle_editor\">\n \n                <p class=\"editor\">(责任编辑：潘静娴_NQ0184)<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":610,"pic":["https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/transform/500/w300h200/20200121/5154-innckce5904108.jpg"],"title":"无论历经多少艰辛 依然爱你如初","type":"1","content":"<p class=\"art_p\">原标题：男友偷偷录了3年的求婚视频爆火：一个男人动了情是什么样子？<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\">作者：彬彬有理<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">最近，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">一支短短不到4分钟的视频，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">在网络上迅速走红。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">视频的主人公杨沛，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">原本只是想记录一下<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">自己准备了3年的<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c嫁给我\u201d求婚视频，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">未曾想吸引了无数人的关注。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">视频来源：微博@杨沛2014<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">目前这条视频在全网<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">总播放量超过4000万，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">很多人都在羡慕<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">这个叫做王园园的女孩，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">纷纷喊话：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">王园园，你到底嫁不嫁？<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">不嫁我嫁了。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">不嫁，我就立刻改名\u201c王园园\u201d。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u2026\u2026<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">我想，这或许就是一个男人<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">最动情的表现\u2014\u2014<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">始终把你放在他的未来里，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">所有的一切小细节都透露着爱。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">01<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">故事的开头很老套<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">\u201c嫁给我吧\u201d的心却很真诚<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">故事的开头，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">要从2016年底说起。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛和女友王园园因工作结识，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">在相处中，他们发现彼此很合拍，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">于是就在2017年年初确定关系。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">相恋半年的时候，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛就有了求婚的想法。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">但是怕太过草率，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">于是他便在女友不知情的情况下，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">从他们第一次旅行开始，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">就开始了这场\u201c预谋\u201d已久的求婚仪式。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2017年7月31日 ，在青海湖，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他支开了王园园，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">在略微抖动的画面和不自然的表情下，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">进行了自己的第一次求婚：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='http://f.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/572/w358h214/20200810/d200-ixreehn4374270.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2017年10月1日，在重庆，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他说：\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/55/w550h305/20200810/ad8f-ixreehn4374349.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2017年12月5日，在杭州，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他说：\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/56/w550h306/20200810/b58c-ixreehn4374381.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2018年9月22日，在西宁，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">这是好朋友的婚礼，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">看着一对新人结婚的幸福模样，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他说：\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/526/w342h184/20200810/ebd3-ixreehn4374421.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2018年10月10日，在门头沟，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">在朋友的生日会上，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他说：\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/526/w342h184/20200810/77e1-ixreehn4374454.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2018年11月29日，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他第一次来到了王园园的家，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">当女友送他回去后，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他又偷偷溜回来，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">对着镜头说：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/526/w342h184/20200810/7245-ixreehn4374492.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2018年12月31日，在崇礼，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他们在滑雪场送走了<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">2018年的最后一天，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他说：<font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/52/w550h302/20200810/0411-ixreehn4374549.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2019年1月21日，在首尔，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">这是两个人第一次在国外跨年，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">王园园兴奋地高喊\u201c新年快乐\u201d，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">而一旁的杨沛笑意盈盈：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/53/w550h303/20200810/b0e4-ixreehn4374578.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">2019年10月10日，在丽贝岛<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">这天杨沛出来晨跑的时候，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">又记录下了这一刻：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/57/w550h307/20200810/6002-ixreehn4374605.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">三年时间，一千多个日夜，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">从第一次旅行到第一次去女友家，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">从朋友婚礼到好友生日，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">从国内到国外\u2026\u2026<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">季节在循环交替，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">身边的人也在来来去去，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">但不变的依然是那句：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">钱钟书曾写给杨绛一段文字：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">\u201c遇到你之前，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">我没想过结婚；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">遇见你以后，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">结婚这事我没想过和别人。\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">正如杨沛一般，<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">真正<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">动情<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">后，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">只有一个念头：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">我爱你，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">便只想和你一起度过余生。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">02<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">甜言蜜语只是1%<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\">而行动代表着一切<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">漫漫人生路，<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">不只有甜，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">更多的是掺杂着生活的烟火气。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">翻看他们的微博，你会发现，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛也是诚诚恳恳的<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">把女友王园园放在心上。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">王园园喜欢倒腾美食，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛则是名副其实的捧场大王，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">总对她的手艺赞不绝口：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c这个锅是精髓，你是灵魂\u201d。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c王氏红烧肉太好吃了。\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/770/w494h276/20200810/effa-ixreehn4374738.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='http://f.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/726/w458h268/20200810/996b-ixreehn4374821.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">当然，<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">爱一个人，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">甜言蜜语只是1%，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">剩下皆是行动。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">只要王园园做饭，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛就会自觉收拾洗碗。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">因为在他心里，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">家是两个人的，家务也是。<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='http://f.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/726/w458h268/20200810/074b-ixreehn4375095.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">在女友面前，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛还是个妥妥的话痨，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">会在旁边分享工作中遇到的开心事，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">好像有说不完的话。<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/770/w494h276/20200810/7f22-ixreehn4375237.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">两个人也会想方设法做些有趣的事，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">比如一起画妆，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">玩玩小游戏。<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/586/w362h224/20200810/fc92-ixreehn4375267.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/498/w320h178/20200810/17f9-ixreehn4375293.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">爱不就是这样吗？<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">在<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">那些<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">看似<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">微不足<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">道的小细节里<\/font>，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">两个人一起吃很多的饭，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">说没必要的废话，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">做别人觉得没必要的事情。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">简简单单，温柔美好。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">像极了杨沛和王园园的爱情。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">03<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">无论历经多少艰辛，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">依然爱你如初<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">原本杨沛计划在女友生日当天求婚，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">但没想到一场突如其来的疫情，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">打乱了他所有的计划。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">女友家住武汉，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">当武汉封城的时候，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他无时无刻不在担心。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">也就是那时候，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他决定在女朋友返回北京的当天求婚。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">今年4月8日，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">为了不妨碍检疫人员工作，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">他特意安排了一场无接触求婚，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">精心准备了求婚车。<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/162/w550h412/20200810/4488-ixreehn4375334.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/116/w550h366/20200810/d1d8-ixreehn4375365.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">当两辆车相遇，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">又见到那张熟悉的面庞，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛终于说出了那句话：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c王园园，嫁给我吧！\u201d<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">话音刚落，<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">女友立马抢答：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u201c我愿意！\u201d<\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/gif_image/192/w639h353/20200810/8a1f-ixreehn4375409.gif' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">那一天，<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛在微博写到：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">2020年4月8日，<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">武汉解封，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">小仙女第一时间回到了北京，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">但下了火车就被隔离车拉走了，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">感谢大家帮我策划了，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">一场无接触式求婚！<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">录制了3年的求婚视频<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">也终于派上了用场！<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">隔窗相望，虽无法相拥，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">但能够看到彼此，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">就已热泪盈眶！<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/251/w550h501/20200810/b846-ixreehn4375446.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">王园园则用一句话，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">回应了男友的用心：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">这三年走过的每一步都算数。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/411/w550h661/20200810/9a2b-ixreehn4374248.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">杨沛表示他们已经决定：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">今年下半年领证，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">明年春天举办婚礼。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">真心为他们开心，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">让我们看到了爱情可以这么美！<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">&nbsp;写给闺蜜：<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">可能你曾经受过伤，<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">不愿意再相信爱情，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">可能你一直在等待，<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">还没有遇到那个人，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\u2026\u2026<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">但请相信：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">爱情这条路，<\/font><\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">或许荆棘丛生，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">或许平坦顺利。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">但总会有人顺着方向<\/font><\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">找到你，<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">把你始终放在他的未来里。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">而你，也要时刻做好准备，<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">随时迎接他的到来。<\/font><\/p>\n<div sax-type=\"proxy\" class=\"j_native_tuv200810 box\" style=\"margin:20px 0\"><\/div><p class=\"art_p\">更多精彩内容敬请关注@新浪女性（微博）<\/p>"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":1374,"pic":["https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/b655da7fp00qexjq5004rc0009c005uc.png"],"title":"41岁李孝利隐退多年 复出仍是韩圈顶流！","type":"1","content":"<div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"page js-page on\">\n              <p>提起韩国娱乐圈中让人无法忽视的女神，李孝利绝对是一座绕不开的大山。近日由41岁的不败女神李孝利、天王Rain及国民主持人刘在石组成的全新唱跳组合\u201cSSAK3\u201d，刚出道就引起了极大的关注度和热烈的风潮。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/8e4f2e02p00qew2ue02mlc0018g00p0c.png\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/8e4f2e02p00qew2ue02mlc0018g00p0c.png'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>虽然李孝利今年已经41岁了，但是她的业务水平和舞台风格依然稳得让人尖叫。就连天王Rain也心甘情愿地蹲在一旁，专心做给姐姐吹风的小迷弟~<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/e7bc0cf9g00qew2xc01fwc000b40069c.gif\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/e7bc0cf9g00qew2xc01fwc000b40069c.gif'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>曾经的\u201c国民妖精\u201d李孝利，如今虽然已过不惑之年，但是身材和外形保持的依然很年轻，谁又能在她身上看得出岁月的痕迹呢？近期登上某时尚杂志封面的李孝利，让大家连连惊叹\u201c当年的女神又回来了\u201d。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/b9ba924bj00qew3el001qc000fa00iqc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/b9ba924bj00qew3el001qc000fa00iqc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>李孝利、Rain和刘在石的组合\u201cSSAK3\u201d从还没组成时，就引发了外界的强烈关注和热议，三人的综艺《闲着干嘛呢》更是获得了超高的收视率。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/1a486ff1j00qexjln001oc000m800dwc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/1a486ff1j00qexjln001oc000m800dwc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>李孝利虽然是作为女团成员之一出道，但是这么多年来一直都作为Solo女歌手活跃在娱乐圈，甚至单独活动时人气也丝毫不低于团队活动。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/a82048d6j00qew3tc0050c000bh00fic.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/a82048d6j00qew3tc0050c000bh00fic.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>当国民女神再次以唱跳团体的身分回归，她那保养得宜的性感身材瞬时成为热议话题。在接受时尚媒体采访的时候，李孝利分享了自己的7大减肥保养秘诀：<\/p><\/div><div class=\"page js-page\"><p>技巧1：控制淀粉，多摄入蛋白质<\/p><p>李孝利表示自己在主食的选择上，与其吃米饭、面食等淀粉类食物，更倾向于摄取蛋白质来补充体内所需的营养。不过李孝利说自己不吃牛、鸡、猪，等\u201c陆上动物\u201d，因此在蛋白质的选择上以更为低脂的海鲜为主。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/d66fbf47j00qexjn0007tc000m800m7c.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/d66fbf47j00qexjn0007tc000m800m7c.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>技巧2：千万别断食！<\/p><p>市面上减肥方法众多，李孝利自己也曾尝试过在韩国风靡一时的\u201c柠檬水减肥法\u201d\u2014\u2014完全断食，只喝柠檬水。这种方法虽然让她在短时间内瘦得很明显，但却也引起了不少身体健康上的副作用，包括精神不振、易疲劳等，甚至整个人的气色都看起来沧桑了很多。<\/p><p>技巧3：每天一杯茶<\/p><p>与其只喝柠檬水地极端断食，李孝利如今会在起床后立马喝上一杯热茶，帮助体内器官快速恢复活力运作，加速新陈代谢。<\/p><p>同时，李孝利也表示自己身为艺人，如果需要在短时间内瘦下来，则会靠\u201c生食减肥法\u201d，她自曝曾经依靠这种方式，在一周内瘦了五公斤。\u201c生食减肥法\u201d是指只吃原模原样、不过度烹煮、不添加任何调味料的天然食物，大多以蔬菜或坚果为主。这种方式不但能够维持体内的充足的纤维营养，也能帮助代谢。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/bdc58063j00qexjgj003lc000hz00dfc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/bdc58063j00qexjgj003lc000hz00dfc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>技巧4：每天练瑜伽<\/p><p>如果你也曾经看过韩国综艺节目《孝利家民宿》，那你一定知道，李孝利有长期练习瑜伽的习惯。不论她前一天睡得多晚，隔天也仍会坚持早起练习瑜伽。瑜伽不但能够舒缓身心灵、帮助减肥瘦身，还可以雕塑身材线条、维持好体态。<\/p><p>技巧5：找到适合自己的运动。<\/p><p>平常热爱舞蹈的李孝利，即使是在非工作活动期间，私下有空也会练习跳舞。她将跳舞视为运动、生活的一部分，由此可见找到自己享受、喜欢的运动有多么的重要！<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/8077958bj00qew3el006lc000c800enc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0811/8077958bj00qew3el006lc000c800enc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><\/div><div class=\"page js-page\"><p>技巧6：心态年轻很重要<\/p><p>而维持身材最重要的一点，当然还是要保持\u201c正面的心态\u201d，以积极乐观的态度面对生活中的一切。心理年龄降低了，外貌体型也会跟着年轻起来，这点真的要和李孝利女神多学习呢！<\/p>\n              <div class=\"otitle_editor\">\n \n                <p class=\"editor\">(责任编辑：刘序_NQ7809)<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>"},{"id":1,"state":1,"pic":"https://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=3070367409,2968608489&fm=26&gp=0.jpg","title":"测试广告1","type":"2","url":"https://www.baidu.com/"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":1088,"pic":["https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd20200811s/520/w925h395/20200811/7a36-ixreehn8544612.jpg"],"title":"比找工作更重要的是找自己！这首MV送给每一个追光的你","type":"1","content":"<p class=\"art_p\">原标题：比找工作更重要的是找自己！这首MV送给每一个追光的你<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"align-Center align-right font-L\"><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"align-Center align-right font-L\"><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><div class=\"img_wrapper\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/559/w1080h1079/20200811/d0df-ixreehn8544202.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/div><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">追<\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><div class=\"img_wrapper\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/559/w1080h1079/20200811/d0df-ixreehn8544202.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/div><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">光<\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><div class=\"img_wrapper\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/559/w1080h1079/20200811/d0df-ixreehn8544202.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/div><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">的<\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><div class=\"img_wrapper\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/559/w1080h1079/20200811/d0df-ixreehn8544202.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/div><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">人<\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><\/p><p class=\"art_p\">盛夏伴随着别离<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">成长又送来一场远行<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">一切过往 皆为序章<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">青春无畏 且歌且行<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">我们怀揣着梦想在那年夏天走入校园<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">而如今<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">迎来了伴着欢笑与泪水<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">与过去四年别离的日子<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">挥手过后<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">我们带着那份梦想<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">走到了人生的十字路口<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">眺望那远处的未知征途<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">或许有些踌躇和迷茫<\/p><div sax-type=\"proxy\" class=\"j_native_stu200811 box\" style=\"margin:20px 0\"><\/div><p class=\"art_p\"><!--单视频_s-->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  <figure class=\"art_video\" data-dataid=\"\" data-ratio=\".56\" data-infos='{\"attrs\":{\"data-tid\":\"38790\",\"data-did\":\"ivhvpwy0465928\",\"data-cid\":\"38790\",\"data-sid\":\"1\",\"data-vid\":\"34739234103\",\"data-adtags\":\"347392341|0|0|0|9805,0|0|9805|0|0|0\",\"data-vLength\":\"232879\",\"data-advid\":\"34739234103\",\"poster\":\"\\/\\/p.ivideo.sina.com.cn\\/video\\/347\\/392\\/341\\/347392341_220_124.jpg\",\"controls\":\"controls\",\"tabindex\":\"0\",\"preload\":\"auto\",\"data-lov\":\"vod\",\"data-vpid\":\"347392341\",\"data-fcid\":\"34739234103\",\"data-livesource\":\"vms\",\"data-liveEditChannel\":\"\",\"data-vot\":\"\",\"data-lt\":\"\",\"data-vd\":\"232879\"},\"baseUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/interface.sina.cn\\/wap_api\\/video_location.d.html?cid=38790&table_id=38790&did=ivhvpwy0465928&vt=4&creator_id=1001_12_0_0&vid=34739234103&video_id=347392341&r=news.sina.cn%2F2020-08-11%2Fdetail-iivhvpwy0465928.d.html\"}'>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  <img  src='https://p.ivideo.sina.com.cn/video/347/392/341/347392341_220_124.jpg' alt=\"\" class=\"img_width\"/>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  <em class=\"art_video_btn cm_c_c j_video_play_btn\"><span class=\"icon_b_video\"><\/span><\/em>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  <\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  <h2 class=\"cm_tit art_video_tit_solo\">比找工作更重要的是找自己！这首MV送给每一个追光的你<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t  <!--单视频_e--><\/p><p class=\"art_p\">在这个从学校走入社会<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">角色发生转变的阶段<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">中国青年报<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">给每一位无畏向前的青年<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">送上这首《追光的人》<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">愿我们永远心怀梦想<br><\/p><p class=\"art_p\">永远热泪盈眶<\/p><p class=\"art_p\">去书写属于我们的未来<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><\/p> \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/473/w383h90/20200811/4300-ixreehn8544272.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/78/w1072h606/20200811/4535-ixreehn8544311.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><div class=\"img_wrapper\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/348/w1080h1668/20200811/d025-ixreehn8544312.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/div><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">\u201c我们就像八九点的太阳<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">我们从此不一样<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">再黑的夜都能找到方向<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">我们无处不在闪耀光芒\u201d<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">回首过去，我们可能有过许多梦想，它们或许很天真，或许很远大，但它们随着我们年龄的增长在变化，而我们也在梦想的变化中一步步成长。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">大学四年的追梦路上，我们也许有过无声的彷徨和挣扎，但无论如何，我们总会重新拥有一往无前的勇气，奋力向前。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">纵使漆黑的苍穹，也有星星微弱的光芒。纵使无助的迷茫，也有梦想坚定的力量。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">我们就这样在一个又一个的黑夜里，找到星光，找到方向。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/77/w1071h606/20200811/b656-ixreehn8544391.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><div class=\"img_wrapper\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/348/w1080h1668/20200811/d025-ixreehn8544312.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/div><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">\u201cNo pain no gain <\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">a better day can be delayed<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">but never too late\u201d<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">追梦，并不会一帆风顺。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">一条路，人烟稀少，孤独难行，却不得不坚持前行，因为它的尽头，种着\u201c梦想\u201d。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">梦想的可贵之处，就在于它的艰难和孤独，即使不被理解、不被肯定，但仍是我们这一路走来，在奋不顾身追求的东西，哪怕万水千山，哪怕岁月迢迢。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">如今，你准备就绪了吗？紧握着这些年汗与泪浇筑出的武器，进入这梦想的战场。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/80/w1074h606/20200811/4fb6-ixreehn8544428.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><div class=\"img_wrapper\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/348/w1080h1668/20200811/d025-ixreehn8544312.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/div><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">\u201c舍不得跟青春再见<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">期待跟梦想快见面<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">绊脚石未必是荆棘<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">错过惊喜怪不坚定<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">听懂青春的旋律<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">它住在未来现在和回忆里\u201d<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">青春短暂如昙花一现，我们结束了青葱难忘的校园时光，\u201c社会人\u201d标签就这么措手不及地被贴上了。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">读书的时候，我们总在盼望长大，可以独立生活，和自己的梦想快快见面，而如今，追梦的旅途已经展现在我们面前。<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">放心，这条路并非布满荆棘，<font cms-style=\"font-L\">等待着我们<\/font>的而是名为\u201c探索\u201d的关卡。<font cms-style=\"font-L\">锁定自己\u201c里程碑\u201d，<\/font>坚定信念，一步一个脚印走下去。正因有梦可依，所以未来可期。<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/473/w383h90/20200811/4300-ixreehn8544272.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">愿有前程可奔赴<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">亦有岁月可回头<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">青年的我们未来将会是一片光明<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">未来的岁月里<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">请勇敢追梦，奋力向前<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">做奔涌的后浪<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">不惧风雨 步履不停<\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">出品人：<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L\">张   坤<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">总监制：毛   浩  董   时<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">监   制：闵   捷  孙   晔<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">策   划：付豪杰<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\"><span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/p><p class=\"art_p\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-right\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-right\"><span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/font><\/font><\/p>"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":371,"pic":["https://n.sinaimg.cn/fo/transform/300/w550h550/20200803/b085-ixeeirz7410282.jpg"],"title":"佛教忍辱与压抑的差别","type":"1","content":"<p class=\"art_p\">问：对治瞋怒之道，心理治疗法鼓励不要压抑内在情绪并建立宣泄的管道，例如在独处时大声叫喊、捶打枕头，或是找合适的对象倾吐，具有\u2018丢出去\u2019的倾向。但是佛法反其道而行，要人们忍一口气并靠自己消化之，属于\u2018吞下去\u2019的忍辱。请问这要如何做到？又忍辱和压抑之间有何区别？<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\">答：面对瞋怒时，心理学采用的方法，是鼓励人们真实面对自己的情绪，让情绪有宣泄的管道，但基本上还是不以伤害自己、他人为原则，避免自残伤人的发生。但这也只是一时的解决与宣泄，当人冷静下来后，还是要回过头来，想想自己为何会情绪波动、问题的症结到底在哪里？从自己的身上找答案。<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\">佛法在对治瞋怒时，给人的印象好像叫人一味的压抑，不该有情绪反应。其实，佛法鼓励面对瞋怒，是采取忍辱，这和压抑是截然不同的态度。表面看起来忍辱只是另种压抑，但忍辱是提醒人们先要态度柔软，柔软的言行可以避免更大的冲突，而非压抑心中不满的情绪；压抑像一颗不定时的炸弹随时有引爆的危机，届时杀伤力更大。忍辱也是慈悲的伸展，慈悲心会帮助人们站在对方立场想，用同理心取代一时宣泄愤怒的快意，取而代之的是理解与谅解。<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\">忍辱不是忍气吞声，也不是逆来顺受，而是在瞋怒当下，退一步替自己也替对方，制造一个足以让彼此回旋的空间，藉由这个空间，让愤怒、委屈、不平的情绪随时间转化。等风平浪静之后，再来整理所发生的事，平静地站在两边的立场来思维，能处理就处理，暂时无法处理，就先放下它。就像要在狂风中扫落叶，只是自讨苦吃，与其对着飞舞的叶子大声咆哮，不如后退一步，耐心等待狂风止息，等落叶纷纷栖息地面，再来处理，就容易多了。　⠀<\/p>\n<div sax-type=\"proxy\" class=\"j_native_lmn200805 box\" style=\"margin:20px 0\"><\/div><p class=\"art_p\">圣严法师说：\u2018修忍辱行，要学习海绵精神，善用智慧处理，以慈悲化解。\u2019一旦面对让自己瞋怒的情境，要如同海绵一样，柔软而坚定，顺着外力、缩小自己，却永恒不失去自己内在的中心点，无论遭遇任何情境，透过忍辱一次又一次冲刷烦恼，直到转烦恼为菩提，让自己的心时常处于平静的状态。⠀<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\">忍辱是以退为进，藉由试炼来转化及超越自己，心胸一旦提升，不再处处与人事碰撞受伤，最后受惠的是自己，是让自己更健康的弹性作法。<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\">\u2014\u2014来源：法鼓文化《人生杂志》270期<\/p>"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":372,"pic":["https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0805/6c5e03fdp00qekivr001wc0009c005uc.png"],"title":"这块劳力士被拍出150万美金 它到底牛在哪？","type":"1","content":"<div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"page js-page on\">\n              <p>近日，一枚稀有劳力士Daytona John Player在苏富比拍卖行以150万美元售出，创下苏富比在线手表拍卖的最新价格记录。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0805/20a8793bp00qekik1008yc000m800f7c.png\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0805/20a8793bp00qekik1008yc000m800f7c.png'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>这款劳力士Daytona 6264\u201cPaul Newman\u201d John Player Special，由于款式稀有珍贵，因此备受收藏家关注。此款手表搭载的是727手上链机芯，表款采用黄金材质，这也确保了它一定的价格水准。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0805/ab6e2faap00qekik100b0c000j600cuc.png\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0805/ab6e2faap00qekik100b0c000j600cuc.png'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0805/b938abcbp00qekik200iuc000ih00dyc.png\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0805/b938abcbp00qekik200iuc000ih00dyc.png'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>另外，此表非常具有稀有性，Paul Newman版本的Daytona本来就相对稀少，而采用K金表壳的版本更是少之又少，尤其是黑面造型。而这款腕表的名字则来自70年代的莲花一级方程式赛车涂装，外观以金色结构配以黑色表盘呈现，尺寸为37毫米，配备727型机芯，旋入式后盖，如今被人发掘到的金色版只有10枚。<\/p>\n              <div class=\"otitle_editor\">\n \n                <p class=\"editor\">(责任编辑：潘静娴_NQ0184)<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":1369,"pic":["https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/transform/500/w300h200/20200813/2bb2-ixreehp5228148.jpg"],"title":"谈恋爱没必要互翻手机吧","type":"1","content":"<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\">原标题：\u201c谈恋爱没必要互翻手机吧\u201d<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\">作者：末那大叔<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">\u201c最糟糕的恋爱关系是什么样的？\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">不管做什么事，总是害怕对方生气；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">在一起的时间里，争吵比甜蜜多；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">因为爱上一个人，变得不喜欢自己了。<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">就像一个海螺，原本自由自在地生活在海滩上；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">却因为寄居蟹的霸占，被控制地丧失了内核，成为傀儡。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">比起出轨、家暴等显性缺点；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">\u201c控制欲\u201d的隐性伤害，才是所有女孩最应该警惕的。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">上海杀妻冰柜藏尸案，凶手朱晓东就是一个控制欲极强的人。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">他曾让妻子辞掉高薪的工作，陪自己去香港；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">还卸载妻子的微信，删除她的异性好友；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">更是在家里安装摄像头，随时监控她的一举一动。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/783/w550h233/20200813/9542-ixreehp5176508.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">所有的一切都是预警，可惜她没能逃脱恶魔的手掌。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">控制欲本身，跟学历、资产、地位等通通无关；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">外表再无害的人，也可能不为人知的一面。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">而那些本可以避免伤害，往往都有迹可循。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">控制欲：★★<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">实时监控你的手机<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\">\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/59/w550h309/20200813/b390-ixreehp5176569.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">读者KIKI讲过一件亲身经历：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">前公司里，有个特别\u201c贴心\u201d的男同事。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">他总能及时知道她的心情，给她点好奶茶；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">甚至周末，两人也经常能偶遇，好感倍增。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">直到有次，她在他的抽屉里，发现了一只熟悉的蓝牙耳机。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">她才终于明白，她在公司\u201c遗失\u201d的那只耳机；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">一直被男同事拿来，监听她的通话内容和微信消息。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">事情过去很久，KIKI想起这个男生，都心有余悸。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">她庆幸自己及时发现了端倪，没有跟男生在一起。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">否则监听手机只是第一步，下一步；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">他不知会把\u201c监控\u201d，装在哪里。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">亲密关系中的\u201c亲密\u201d是结果，而非前提；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">10倍速靠近你的人，一定要小心他的用意。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">控制欲：★★★<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">贬低你、逼你改变<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\">\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/112/w550h362/20200813/c9bb-ixreehp5176627.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">控制欲强的人都有自卑感，很容易患得患失；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">因为害怕对方的离开，会想方设法让对方自我怀疑。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">电影《煤油灯下》，男主送给女主一个首饰，又偷偷拿走。<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">目的是为了让她怀疑自己记性不好，充满内疚。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">男主又在家里制造响动，让灯光忽明忽暗；<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">目的是为了让她觉得，自己\u201c精神失常\u201d、病了。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/68/w550h318/20200813/4d4e-ixreehp5176680.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">逐渐地，她从一个有主见、自信的女孩，变得敏感脆弱。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">彻底变成了他的战利品，离不开他了。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">如果你发现，因为跟一个人在一起，而多了很多缺点；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">一定要警觉，是不是日常遭受了太多打压。<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">以贬低你的价值，而捆绑的关系；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">一定有利可图，但受益者一定不是你。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">控制欲：★★★<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">限制你社交<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\">\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/56/w550h306/20200813/fcff-ixreehp5176764.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">演员海陆的前任，是个控制欲爆棚的人：<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">平时，他不仅要跟海陆打着电话睡觉；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">还会趁她不注意，把她手机里的异性朋友都删掉。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/86/w550h336/20200813/f030-ixreehp5176864.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">以至于海陆后来参加节目，遇见熟悉的男化妆师；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">打招呼不是说\u201c好久不见\u201d，而是先说抱歉。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">太过懂事的姑娘，在矛盾面前擅长妥协；<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">却往往忘了，一味地退让只会让对方得寸进尺。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">有研究表明：成年人谈一场恋爱，会丢失三个朋友；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">是因为我们把生活重心，偏向了喜欢的人。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">但如果对方要求，你的世界里只有他。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">那不是爱情，是霸凌。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\">&nbsp;04&nbsp;<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">控制欲：★★★★★<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">对你进行人身控制<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\">\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/59/w550h309/20200813/adc4-ixreehp5176904.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">电影《隐形人》中，讲述了一个控制狂变态。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">他不允许女友跟任何人来往、交谈；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">从精神和肉体上，对她进行双重控制。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">甚至在女友逃跑后，佯装死亡；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">然后穿着\u201c隐身衣\u201d，24小时潜伏在她的身边。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/215/w550h465/20200813/af82-ixreehp5176957.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">跟这样的伴侣在一起，轻则是丢掉生活；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">重则是丢了性命、毁了人生。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">爱情需要磨合，而不是一味配合；<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">需要倾听，而不是无条件听从。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">需要理解，而不是一意孤行。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">有人说《三十而已》里，顾佳控制欲太强：<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">不让许幻山踢球、吃完饭甚至管他穿什么。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">可事实是，她是他事业上最靠谱的伙伴。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">她不让许幻山吃晚饭，是因为他有脂肪肝。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">况且他有多少顿不吃，她都一一陪着。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/145/w550h395/20200813/4e78-ixreehp5177041.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">居心叵测的人，总喜欢把\u201c控制欲\u201d包装成爱；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">然后打着\u201c害怕失去\u201d的旗号，肆意伤害。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">真正的爱，是盼你好，也让你好。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">是你能肉眼可见地看到，自己往高处走。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/599/w550h849/20200813/f621-ixreehp5177099.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">如何避免陷入\u201c被控制\u201d的爱情中？<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">北大心理学博士李松蔚，言简意赅地说：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">\u201c如果一段亲密关系让你感觉不舒服，你是可以离开的。\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">不要总是自责，是不是两人磨合地不好；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">怀疑自己太矫情、要求太多。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">也不用按照PUA的条例，一条条匹配；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">怕自己误解了对方的好意，怕自己太过敏感。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">记住只要\u201c不舒服\u201d，就可以选择离开；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">这不是绝情，而是一种自我保护。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">如果无底线的听从、信任一个人。<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">你将永远不知道是置身花海，还是身在危楼。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">等着你的是彩虹，<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L\">还是天<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L\">台；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">你还有很长的一生，那应该是很好的一生。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">如果爱情不能雪中送炭，我希望你大胆单身；<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">自由、快乐、平安。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\">更多精彩内容敬请关注@新浪女性（微博）<\/p>"},{"id":2,"state":1,"pic":"https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&quality=80&size=b9999_10000&sec=1597255357871&di=25231d3d624faf040cf1718228148bec&imgtype=0&src=http%3A%2F%2Ffile.youboy.com%2Fa%2F105%2F81%2F6%2F2%2F11099982s.jpg","title":"测试广告2","type":"2","url":"http://news.baidu.com/"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":366,"pic":["https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/transform/500/w300h200/20200731/6a0f-ixeeiry9723004.jpg"],"title":"爱情应该是锦上添花 而不是非他不可","type":"1","content":"<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">原标题：\u201c你们一南一北，互不干涉\u201c：不婚主义从来不等于开放伴侣！<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\">作者：陆琪 &nbsp;<\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">当你三十岁的时候，遇到了一个不愿意结婚的男人怎么办？<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">之前罗志祥被称为\u201c时间管理大师\u201d，如今又出现了一个新词\u2014\u2014<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">空间管理大师<\/font><\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L\">。<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/23/w550h273/20200803/02e4-ixeeirz8536748.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">01<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">见过了陈屿的冷暴力，骂过了许幻山的出轨，梁正贤也不甘示弱。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">游轮上一见钟情的王漫妮，原以为自己等了这么久，终于等到了那个对的人，却不想等来的竟是一个不婚主义的\u201c海王\u201d。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">梁正贤从和王漫妮在一起开始，就一直强调自己是一个<\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">\u201c不婚主义者\u201d<\/font><\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L\">，而王漫妮一直觉得只要自己坚持，也许能够改变他的想法、步入婚姻。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">因为对于她来说，梁正贤是一个满足她对恋爱所有期待的男人。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">但是这所有的美好幻想都被梁正贤所谓的\u201c未婚妻\u201d所打破，得知真相的王漫妮才知道自己只不过是他众多鱼塘中，一条被喂养的小鱼而已。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">对此梁正贤的说法很可笑：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">你们两个，一南一北，互不干涉。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">我是个不婚主义，这就是开放式伴侣的态度。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/250/w509h541/20200803/17f5-ixeeirz8536777.png' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">打着\u201c不婚主义\u201d的幌子，只是为了不用对一段感情负责。就算有一天厌倦了，也可以无所顾忌地抽身离开，说白了就只是不想负责罢了。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">而梁正贤也因为这样的言论，被冠上了\u201c空间管理大师\u201d的名字。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">真正的不婚主义是确定自己不会结婚，更不想去经营一段感情，而所谓的开放伴侣，不过是一种\u201c伪不婚主义\u201d。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">不婚主义从来不等于开放伴侣，这是两种不能被混淆的概念。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">不能否认会有这样一部分不婚主义者的存在，但其实大部分的人都很容易感受到孤独，所以大部分的人还是需要爱、需要家庭的。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">所以，哪有什么不婚主义，只是他没那么爱你而已。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">既然这个世界大部分的人都需要爱、需要家庭，可为什么还有有很多人不愿意结婚呢？<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">02<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">@不吃草的兔子<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">\u201c我很享受一个人的现在，想不通为什么要结婚\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">她是一个26岁至今单身的女生，大学一毕业就自己创业，开了一家小规模的策划公司，如今也算是小有成绩。除了工作，她会用剩余的时间健身、旅行，按照她自己的话来说，根本没有谈恋爱的时间和欲望。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">对于她现在拥有的生活，她觉得充实又有意思，家中养了两只猫，也从未觉得孤独。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">其实这也是很多在都市打拼的年轻人现状，养着宠物、偶尔和三两个好友约会、一个人生活。即便偶尔也会觉得寂寞，但是却很享受这样没有拘束的独居生活。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">一个人的时候可以做任何自己想做的事，见任何自己想见的人，去任何自己想去的地方。两个人却要开始考虑对方的感受，甚至会为了对方约束自己。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">享受孤独，害怕两个人的生活，是很多恐婚人的正常心理。<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/129/w500h429/20200519/7904-itvqcca5054383.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">03<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">@贝加加的花园<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">\u201c恋爱可能会比结婚更幸福\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">她有男朋友，却不想要结婚。并不是因为她不想对这段感情开始负责，也不是因为她想要给自己留有更多的机会，而是害怕婚姻会让爱情消散。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">她说：与其为了结婚的琐事而吵到分手、与其在婚后因为柴米油盐消褪了激情，倒不如享受恋爱的现状，至少在拥有纯粹爱情的时候，我们是幸福的就够了。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">身边有很多人都是这样，明明谈了一段很稳定的恋爱，可到了结婚都会谈崩。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">朋友说有一个学长前段时间发了婚礼的请柬，最近却突然通知婚礼取消了、不办了。后来才知道原因是女方要求他拿出30万的彩礼，两家争执不下干脆取消了婚礼。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">最令人尴尬的是，原本收获祝福的学长，需要一个个通知那些收到请柬的人婚礼取消。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">所以你看，婚姻真的不能保障爱情。有多少相爱多年的情侣，总是过不了\u201c结婚\u201d那道坎。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">但是这句话用到梁正贤的身上却并不合适，因为他只不过是用不结婚来掩饰自己的花心，毕竟一个\u201c已婚\u201d的男人，便很难再养起自己的鱼塘。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">有些人不结婚，是为了更好的经营爱情，而有些人不结婚，只是为了拥有多段爱情。<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/59/w550h309/20200511/2384-itmiwry9122034.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">04<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">@木十一<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">\u201c原生家庭的缺憾，让我害怕结婚这件事\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">有人说他是个渣男，明明凭借外表就可以吸引很多女生，但偏\u201c万花丛中过，片叶不沾身\u201d，一定是为了给更多的女生留机会。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">但其实他只是因为从小父母的离异，让他对婚姻产生了一种恐惧的心理。从记事起，父母永远都在争吵，极端的时候甚至会动手砸东西。后来他们离婚了，母亲直接丢下了他独自离开了。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">所以在他眼里，婚姻这件事带来的一直都是负面的影响。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">因为他们在过去也曾那么相爱，可是在婚后却吵得不可开交，所以结婚并不能保证一个家庭的完整，即便再相爱的也难免会发生争吵。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">与其在得到后感受失去的痛苦，倒不如从未得到过。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">原生家庭对一个人的影响，是不可磨灭的。但是如果因为害怕失败而不去接受爱情，其实也是一种逃避。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">如果你没有尝过爱情的甜，你一定不能轻易给它下了\u201c苦\u201d的定义，所以我们总是会说这样一句话，要具备接受爱情的勇气。<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/732/w440h292/20200803/cdb6-ixeeirz8536901.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">05<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">陆琪老师在说《喜宝》这本书的时候有一句话：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">第一她要爱，很多很多的爱，第二她要钱，很多很多的钱，第三，她要健康。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">其实很多人都是一样，他们第一个想要的就是爱，但正是因为想要得到什么，所以才更会害怕失去什么。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">就比如最近的《二十不惑》和《三十而已》来说，一个是年轻人的爱恨情仇，一个是经历过婚姻打磨的三十岁女人，很显然爱情所带来的的快乐可能超过婚姻。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">所以与其承受婚姻所带来的的不确定性，更多人宁愿享受当下。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">但其实我们都陷入了一个误区：<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">当爱情来临的时候，总会担心眼前这个人在往后的日子里是否依然会像现在一样爱我；<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">当面对婚姻的时候，总会担心这个说要跟自己共度一生的人是不是会说离开就离开。<\/font><\/p>\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/eladies/crawl/105/w550h355/20200803/67ae-ixeeirz8536936.jpg' alt=\"\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\"><\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">却从来没有想过两个人在一起不是你成为他的附属品，他的存在也许会让你过得更好，可就算他离开你自己也可以活的很好。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">如果你成为一个这样的人，便不会害怕任何失去，因为你足以照顾好自己。<\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">爱情应该是锦上添花，而不是非他不可。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">如果你需要爱、需要家，那就勇敢去追；如果你还没有遇到那个人，那就再等一等。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">不勉强、不将就，仅此而已。<\/font><\/font><\/p>\n<p class=\"art_p\">更多精彩内容敬请关注@新浪女性（微博）<\/p>"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":1375,"pic":["https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/c318b539p00qexexs00lhc000u600k4c.png"],"title":"加拿大鹅第一财季收入大跌63% ","type":"1","content":"<div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"page js-page on\">\n              <p>据智通财经报道，8月11日美股盘前，高端冬季服装制造商加拿大鹅控股公司(GOOS.US)公布了2021财年第一季度财报。公布财报后，该股盘前下跌，截至北京时间19:37，跌2.66%，报24.15美元。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/44170466j00qexere001qc000u600k4c.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/44170466j00qexere001qc000u600k4c.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>该公司一季度总营收2610万加元，同比下跌63.3%，去年同期为7110万加元；净亏损5010万加元，去年同期为2940万加元；摊薄每股亏损0.46加元，去年同期为0.27加元。调整后净亏损3840万加元，同比扩大68%；调整后摊薄每股亏损0.35加元，去年同期为0.21加元；调整后EBIT为4650万加元，去年同期为2590万加元。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/d8845aecj00qexetd002ec000go009dc.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/d8845aecj00qexetd002ec000go009dc.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>该公司表示，虽然业绩已逐步改善，但2021财年第二季度仍受公共卫生事件影响，预计营收将大幅下降。<\/p><p>鉴于目前对市场的不确定性，同时考虑到第二波公共卫生事件爆发的可能性、零售业复苏的速度以及经济发展的影响和旅行限制对非必需消费支出的影响，该公司暂不提供2021财年业绩指引。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/a380bc4fj00qexepx000uc000fe00a0c.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/a380bc4fj00qexepx000uc000fe00a0c.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div><p>加拿大鹅（Canada Goose）是一家加拿大高端冬季服装制造商，创建于1957年，得名自九大湖地区的特色物种加拿大雁。主要产品有各类夹克、派克大衣、背心、帽子、手套等，在中国市场曾很受欢迎。该品牌因夹克领子使用了郊狼皮毛<font face=\"sans-serif\" color=\"#202122\">，<\/font>曾引起过动物权利保护者的抗议。<\/p><div class=\"photo\">\n                  <a href=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/8ed41946j00qexeso0010c000dv0099c.jpg\">\n                      <img alt=\"\" src='http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0812/8ed41946j00qexeso0010c000dv0099c.jpg'>\n                      <span><\/span>\n                  <\/a>\n              <\/div>\n              <div class=\"otitle_editor\">\n \n                <p class=\"editor\">(责任编辑：刘序_NQ7809)<\/p>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>"},{"see":0,"focus":"0","id":1378,"pic":["https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/799/w509h290/20200811/e774-ixreehn9028878.jpg"],"title":"\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d成梗之后，年轻人还有矫情的权利吗？","type":"1","content":"<p class=\"art_p\"><span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">网易云音乐的用户留言，曾经因为其真诚的情感、动人的故事而\u201c出圈\u201d，被制作成大幅地铁海报、印满矿泉水瓶身，也让更多喜爱同一首歌的人在听歌时找到共鸣。但这种情绪很快滑向另一个极端，留言区开始出现大量或复制粘贴、或不知所云、或\u201c无病呻吟\u201c的评论。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\"><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">全<\/font><\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">文3834字<\/font><\/font><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">，阅读约<\/font><\/font><\/font><font cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">需8分钟 <\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">文/肖舒妍 编辑 西西 徐伟 校对 陈荻雁<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\"><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">这段时间，一个新的网络词汇成为各个社交平台网友二次创作的热点\u2014\u2014\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d。这个词从音乐产品\u201c网易云音乐\u201d谐音而来，用以嘲讽这款软件每首歌曲下的高赞用户留言都充满悲伤、悔恨与泪水，除了爱而不得、高考失利、身患绝症，就连近视、遛狗、拔智齿等常人眼中的小事，也能解读出\u201c此恨绵绵无绝期\u201d的苦痛，简直到了\u201c人均抑郁症\u201d的地步。<\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/799/w509h290/20200811/e774-ixreehn9028878.jpg' alt=\"▲在社交媒体上流传的\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d表情包。\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\">▲在社交媒体上流传的\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d表情包。<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">网易云音乐的用户留言，曾经因为其真诚的情感、动人的故事而\u201c出圈\u201d，被制作成大幅地铁海报、印满矿泉水瓶身，也让更多喜爱同一首歌的人在听歌时找到共鸣、获得慰藉。但是这种情绪很快滑向了另一个极端，留言区开始出现大量或复制粘贴、或不知所云、或\u201c无病呻吟\u201d的评论。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">而另一群原本喜爱这首歌曲或个性较真的网友则开始了\u201c反击\u201d，对这些评论给出了\u201c打破矫情气氛\u201d的科学解释性回复，或是干脆把\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d作为一个梗来嘲讽、二次创作，将网易云的留言称作\u201c分享你刚编的抑郁症故事\u201d、\u201c0点了，可以开始网抑云了\u201d。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">原本的真情流露是怎么转变为\u201c无病呻吟\u201d的？伤痛文学式文字为什么有那么多人喜爱又那么多人痛恨？在\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d式的矫情成为被吐槽的对象之后，我们还有表达脆弱的权利吗？<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">曾经的\u201c树洞\u201d，如今的\u201c点赞量\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/87/w872h815/20200811/f4e4-ixreehn9028938.jpg' alt=\"▲电影《海上钢琴师》（1998）剧照。\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\">▲电影《海上钢琴师》（1998）剧照。<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">音乐，可能是最能唤起情绪的媒介之一。不经意跑进耳朵的一段旋律，就能让你回想起某个熟悉的场景，偶然瞥到的一句歌词，就能让你代入自己的某段故事。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">音乐喜好，也可能是一个人最隐秘、最私人的收藏。一份歌单，就代表着听歌者的个性、品味、此刻的心情、当下所处的人生阶段。即使身处人群熙熙攘攘的地铁，戴上耳机，播放喜爱的歌曲，就能进入专属自己一人的世界。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">这两个因素相加，让音乐播放器中每首歌的留言区都成为了大型\u201c树洞\u201d\u2014\u2014人们听着音乐进入自己的小世界，当某段回忆伴随着情绪被音乐勾起，他们便在留言区写下这段往事和此刻的心情。没有人知道这段留言背后的人是谁，这首歌却可以成为这个故事的注脚和背景音。<\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/206/w1080h726/20200811/87d3-ixreehn9028937.jpg' alt=\"▲电影《乐魂》（1995）剧照。\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\">▲电影《乐魂》（1995）剧照。<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">\u201c树洞\u201d的意义还在于你不仅可以分享自己的感想，更可以看到无数个和你有着相似经历或相同感受的故事。在世上有一些人，和你听着同一首歌，在同一个平台写下了自己的心情，便带来了\u201c天涯觅知音\u201d的快乐，和\u201c我不是自己一个人\u201d的安慰。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">同时，写下的留言右上角，还有一个小小的大拇指，大拇指每被点亮一次，就代表对你多一次的认可、喜爱、鼓励或是安慰。爱心下的数字不断增长，也带来更多写下留言、表达感想的动力。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">但是量变产生质变，当数字从1跳到10，从10跳到100，就像眼前挂着永远吃不到的胡萝卜一样，一些原本有感而发写下留言的听歌者，在下次提笔之前开始反复思考，什么样的故事才能引发更多共情？什么样的表达才会有更多人点赞？<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">于是，就有了现在被称为\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d风格的留言。从讲述自己的真实故事，变为夸张、捏造一段经历；从表达涌起的真实情感，变为放大情绪、无病呻吟；当自己文思枯竭，便引用名人名言；实在才华有限，干脆复制粘贴。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">有人历尽沧桑般写道：\u201c这首歌不知不觉就听十年了，十年前，我还上初三。\u201d尽管这首歌曲刚刚发布，十年前这位歌手可能还没出道，这条留言却获得了近一千次点赞。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">也有人故作老练：\u201c安眠药一盒150，帕罗西汀一盒236，氟西丁一盒472，喜太乐一盒569，氟伏沙明一盒398。\u201d报菜名般一连串报出几种治疗抑郁症药物的价格，来暗示自己罹患抑郁症多年，甚至过量服用药物的经历。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">伤感的情绪泛滥到最后，已经有人开始\u201c浪漫化\u201d抑郁：\u201c抑郁症真是这世上最温柔的病，因为它只伤害自己，不伤害别人。\u201d\u201c我很庆幸我活着，因为活着可以让我好好享受孤独和抑郁这种美妙的感觉。\u201d<\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/51/w1080h571/20200811/fb54-ixreehn9028979.jpg' alt=\"▲根据太宰治同名原著改编的电影《人间失格》（2010）剧照。\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\">▲根据太宰治同名原著改编的电影《人间失格》（2010）剧照。<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">太宰治的\u201c生而为人，我很抱歉\u201d被引用了无数次、演绎出无数个不同版本，鲁迅则被编造了一句\u201c第一次见一个人，体温在38.6℃就叫做一见钟情。\u201d尽管在鲁迅生活的年代，国内使用的温度单位是华氏度\u2014\u2014℉。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">这些留言无一例外都获得了惊人的点赞数。曾经充满真情实感的\u201c树洞\u201d，就在流量的裹挟下成为了贩卖情绪、制造矫情的\u201c网抑云\u201d。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><\/font>当\u201c矫情\u201d遇上\u201c反矫情\u201d<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">不难理解\u201c网抑云\u201d式的留言为何招人反感。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">一方面，任何所谓\u201c金句\u201d都经不起脱离情境的过度解读。张爱玲用\u201c爱就是不问值得不值得\u201d，来表达自己对笔下作品的热爱，甘愿用三十年时间反复改写。可是这句话单拎出来放到留言区，就变成了男女之间愿为对方\u201c卑微到尘埃里\u201d的爱情。再者，再文采斐然见解深刻的段落，复制粘贴几百次占据所有歌曲的留言区之后，都会变得廉价从而引发审美疲劳和反感。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">另一方面，某种流行发展到一定阶段（姑且把\u201c矫情文学\u201d算作一种流行），都会自然出现一种反其道而行的模式与其对立、将其消解，就像曾经的\u201c鸡汤文学\u201d与之后的\u201c毒鸡汤\u201d，曾经的\u201c打鸡血\u201d与之后的\u201c丧文化\u201d。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\"><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">问题是，最初喜爱\u201c矫情文学\u201d、大量为\u201c网抑云\u201d式留言点赞的到底是谁呢？<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">他们可能是每一个曾经年轻、稚气、不谙世事的你我。<\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/61/w1080h581/20200811/7a96-ixreehn9028978.jpg' alt=\"▲\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\">▲<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L align-Center\">电影短片11度青春之《老男孩》（2010）剧照。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">对于这类\u201c矫情文学\u201d的共情，与所处的人生阶段有直接的关系。根据2019年8月发表的《极光：国内在线音乐社区研究报告》显示，网易云音乐25岁以下的年轻用户占比高达83. 5％。25岁以下人群中也包括正在小学、初中、高中或者刚刚进入大学的青年。他们正处于迷茫、敏感又情感丰富的状态，\u201c为赋新词强说愁\u201d，生活中没有大起大落也没有经历过真正的困境，只好在日常小事中倾注内心奔涌的情绪，放大任何细小的挫折。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">例如其中一条留言写道，\u201c15岁，前天刚刚被测出单眼近视175度，现在很绝望，因为医生说会伴随一辈子，一想到这个我就很害怕，也想哭。也开导不了自己，能帮我开导一下吗？真的很害怕。\u201d只不过是单眼175度的近视，甚至不需要佩戴眼镜，但在这句留言中却表现了罹患癌症、生命所剩无几般强烈的绝望。<\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/461/w904h357/20200811/6ba3-ixreehn9029033.jpg' alt=\"▲网易云音乐的一则留言。\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\">▲网易云音乐的一则留言。<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">而处于青春期的年轻人，渴望叛逆，标新立异，也许根本不理解抑郁症的病理，只知道这种疾病父辈羞于提起，便拿来挂在嘴边，当作自己\u201c温柔的标签\u201d。当他们听着自己喜欢的歌曲，在留言区看到类似\u201c45°角仰望天空，不让泪水流下\u201d之类的句子，便顿感心有戚戚。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">在阅历更为丰富或想法更为成熟的另一群用户看来，这样的情绪自然无法理解，和背负房贷、惨遭裁员、子欲养而亲不待等真正的人生遗憾比起来，单眼近视甚至连鸡毛蒜皮的小事儿都算不上，生活中大有比伤春悲秋、小情小爱来得重要、来得宽广的事在。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">于是他们大笔一挥，开始给\u201c网抑云\u201d拆台。比如在\u201c有时候我真的很羡慕鱼，没有温度也没有心跳，只有七秒钟的记忆\u201d这条留言下，有网友开始科普：\u201c首先，温度是一个强度量，它是一直存在的，只有高低之分。其次，鱼也是有心脏和心跳的，用来运输水中含量较低的分子\u2026\u2026\u201d<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">而在其他社交媒体，则有网友开始模仿\u201c网抑云\u201d的表达方式，把生活中的一切都\u201c矫情化\u201d，用\u201c以毒攻毒\u201d来对此表达嘲讽。遛狗时不小心松开了牵引绳，用\u201c网抑云\u201d的表达就是，\u201c连狗绳都抓不住的我，怎么抓得住爱情。\u201d<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">但是嘲讽\u201c网抑云\u201d的这群用户，可能本身也经历过热爱\u201c青春疼痛文学\u201d的阶段，只不过当时这些稚嫩、青涩的表达留在了日记、人人网或者QQ空间里。而现在他们反对这种\u201c矫情文学\u201d，希望的是摆脱当年幼稚的、无知的自己，又或是对这些仍然不谙世事的、实际上无忧无虑的青年带着点\u201c羡慕嫉妒恨\u201d。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold align-Center\"><\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"strong-Bold font-L align-Center\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\">年轻人有表达脆弱的权利吗？<\/font><\/font><\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">不论是嘲讽还是科普，真正喜爱\u201c网抑云\u201d式留言的用户并不会借此试图去理解反对者的想法，这些反对\u201c网抑云\u201d的声音也不能让留言者走出伤春悲秋，只会让双方的隔阂越来越深。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">在这场争论中，随着\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d成为一个流行的新梗，尽管人们笑着提到\u201c人均抑郁症\u201d时，不会隐射或联想到真正的抑郁症患者，但是无意间，作为一种心理疾病的抑郁症，就经历了从\u201c浪漫化\u201d到\u201c污名化\u201d，一开始是\u201c世界上最温柔的疾病\u201d，又变成了\u201c网抑云\u201d用户用来表达矫情的标签。<\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/519/w795h524/20200811/1cda-ixreehn9029032.jpg' alt=\"▲网络流行\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d表情包。\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\">▲网络流行\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d表情包。<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">对\u201c网抑云\u201d的嘲讽和抵制，影响到甚至伤害到的，更可能是真正想要表达脆弱、需要共情与安慰又缺乏勇气的人。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">在白日的工作生活中，他们被要求做一个\u201c情绪稳定的成年人\u201d，等到下班回家，终于拥有属于自己的时间与空间，在喜爱的音乐陪伴下卸下防备，释放情绪，想要在歌曲下留言，却又因为对\u201c网抑云\u201d的嘲讽突然警醒，一个字一个字删除了刚刚敲下的几句话，再三反省自己是不是太过\u201c矫情\u201d，本就为数不多的情绪表达窗口又被堵上。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">这种大型嘲讽像是一种\u201c杀一儆百\u201d，不仅让\u201c矫情\u201d的留言成为了靶子，也吓退了许多还未表达的真实情感，让判断\u201c矫情\u201d的标准越来越低。这也是为什么越来越多人的朋友圈从半年可见到三天可见最后终于仅自己可见。自己当下真实的情感流露，在某个不知前后语境的好友来看，可能就是\u201c无病呻吟\u201d，就像\u201c网抑云\u201d中尼采常被引用的\u201c金句\u201d所说，\u201c那些听不见音乐的人，认为跳舞的人都疯了。\u201d<\/font><\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"art_img_mini j_p_gallery\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"art_img_mini_img j_fullppt_cover\"  src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020811s/679/w693h786/20200811/fb3a-ixreehn9029061.jpg' alt=\"▲电影《雨中曲》（1952）剧照。\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"art_img_tit\">▲电影《雨中曲》（1952）剧照。<\/h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">可是表达脆弱真的是可耻的吗？谁又能时刻百毒不侵油米不进呢？此前一些抑郁症患者难以克服的\u201c病耻感\u201d，现在却出现在了人们面对自己的负面情绪时。来自他人和自己过高的要求与压力，让人变得不敢也不会表达脆弱。尽管脆弱和失落，就像坚强和快乐一样正常。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">而对于网易云音乐而言，\u201c网抑云阴乐\u201d这个绰号无疑会消解用户对音乐的共情和对平台的归属感，曾经包容所有情绪的\u201c树洞\u201d，现在却可能招来嘲讽和谩骂。好在网易云的反应还算迅速，推出了新的\u201c云村公约\u201d，既反对编造抄袭，也禁止嘲讽谩骂，邀请了心理专家和心理学专业志愿者为真正的负面情绪提供帮助，相比标着数字的点赞，只有个人能收到的\u201c拍拍\u201d功能也许能带来流量之外真实的安慰。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L\">音乐与分享，本来就可以治愈的。<\/font><\/p><p class=\"art_p\" cms-style=\"font-L\"><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><\/font><\/p><font cms-style=\"font-L strong-Bold\"><\/font><p class=\"art_p\"><span class=\"img_descr\"><\/span><\/p>"}],"categoryArr":[{"name":"关注","categoryid":17},{"name":"推荐","categoryid":16},{"name":"女性","categoryid":1},{"name":"育儿","categoryid":2},{"name":"政治","categoryid":3},{"name":"财经","categoryid":4},{"name":"体育","categoryid":5},{"name":"娱乐","categoryid":6}]}
     * errmsg : 执行成功
     */

